ZH: 我的狗有一百五十磅。
EN: My dog weighs 150 pounds.

ZH: 这本书有五磅重。
EN: This book weighs five pounds.

ZH: 我的行李箱超过了五十磅的重量限制。
EN: My suitcase exceeds the fifty-pound weight limit.

ZH: 这个橘子大概有半磅。
EN: This orange probably weighs half a pound.

ZH: 他每周锻炼四次，已经减掉了十磅。
EN: He exercises four times a week and has lost ten pounds.

ZH: 这件礼物的实际重量超过了十磅。
EN: The actual weight of this gift exceeds ten pounds.

ZH: 这个婴儿刚出生时只有六磅。
EN: This baby was only six pounds when born.

ZH: 这个西瓜超过了二十磅。
EN: This watermelon weighs over twenty pounds.

ZH: 这家餐馆的特色菜每份都有三磅。
EN: The signature dish of this restaurant comes in three-pound portions.

ZH: 老虎目前已经长到两百五十磅。
EN: The tiger has grown to two hundred and fifty pounds.

ZH: 捐助者支付每磅食物的价格。
EN: Donors pay the price per pound of food.

ZH: 这箱苹果总共有六十磅。
EN: There are sixty pounds of apples in this box.

ZH: 这座雕塑的重量是三千磅。
EN: The weight of this sculpture is three thousand pounds.

ZH: 这块黄金价值每磅超过一万美元。
EN: This piece of gold is worth over ten thousand dollars per pound.

ZH: 这匹马拉着一辆犁，增加了它的体重。
EN: This horse pulling a plow has gained weight.

ZH: 这家超市销售一磅装的新鲜面包。
EN: This supermarket sells fresh bread by the pound.

ZH: 这头大象体重高达两万磅。
EN: This elephant weighs up to twenty thousand pounds.

ZH: 这个年轻的运动员训练后增加了五磅。
EN: This young athlete gained five pounds after training.

ZH: 他决定减肥，目标是减掉十磅。
EN: He decided to lose weight with a goal of shedding ten pounds.

ZH: 这个行李箱有托运时限制，不能超过九十磅。
EN: This suitcase has a weight limit for checked baggage of ninety pounds.
